Text: \<sigh> Desperate times, as they say... I'll summon the defective mammets.
I'm sorry, the what!?
うわぁーっ、こっちに来ないでくださいよーっ！！
仕方ない、こうなったら自爆させるしか……！
Ahaha! Poison here, poison there, poison, poison, everywhere!
Leave this to me, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>. Just keep an eye on Ellerete!
我が部族の秘技、その目に焼きつけなさい！
You are rotten to the core! Why do you persist!?
Godsdamn it all...
I'll handle the rest, Kokonowa! Be a good little goldsmith and sit this out!
No, no, NO! My tonics... They've betrayed me!
Pesky pest problems call for alchemical solutions!
Stubborn worms! I will end you─do you hear me!?

If there are any meaner beasties, they must be biding their time. All I see here is fodder.
Though for practicing your new skills, they'll do fine.
I'll stay outta your way, and give you a few pointers.
Lemme know when you're ready.
Not bad at all! These techniques are some of the most important tools in your kit.
C'mon over here, and I'll tell you about attacking from Dual Fang stance.
You can wrap up your combination with Flanksting Strike, Flanksbane Fang, Hindsting Strike, or Hindsbane Fang.
Open a sequence with Steel Fangs or Dread Fangs and work your way up to one of the four finishers.
Good work, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>. Looks like you got the hang of Dual Fang stance.
That roar just now... Almost like it was telling 'em to clear out.
I reckon there's a big ol' bastard waiting in the wings. And now it's sent us tougher opposition!
Lucky for you, I got just the thing for dealing with lummoxes like them. I'll tell you all about it when you're ready.
Viper stance allows you to use your dual blades as a single weapon and bring everything you've got to bear!
You can even swap back into Dual Fang stance for Twinfang Bite or Twinblood Bite.
Alright, you got the hang of viper, I'd say.
That roaring's getting closer. Boss beast must be pissed that its minions keep getting beat.
Heh, and there it is!
Time to take it down a peg or three. Just remember what you're dealing with here─it ain't no pushover like the rest.
Still, you got all the tools you need at your disposal.
Show it what a viper can do!
Unrelenting attacks are the key! Don't give your prey a chance to fight back!
Some attacks work better from certain positions, so mind your footwork!
Defeat Iq Soq Xmajun!
Iq Soq Xmajun! Give me a bloody spectacle!
I would hate for this to end too quickly. Why not toy with them a little?
Worthy foes indeed... Iq Soq Xmajun, the time for games is over!
What was that!? Some underhanded tactic, no doubt...
Is this the limit of your power!? Kill them! Now!
Move, you great brute, move!
Do as I say! Tear them asunder!
We can't afford any mistakes! Stay sharp, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>!
Wait─what's that smell?
Something's wrong with Iq Soq Xmajun. Don't tell me...
That's it! Innocent Stork's made a huge mistake!
Looks like it's through messing around. Keep it together!
That packed a punch!
So it's gathered some kinda energy in its wings... Can't take too many hits like that!
Golias is right. When it spreads its wings, get ready for a huge attack!
C'mon! Together, now!
Go for the wings! Keep it pinned down!
You did it! Now for the other wing!
That did the trick!
Don't hold back! It won't escape me again!
It's acting strangely! Be careful!
Godsdammit... This ain't over, not by a long shot!
<split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>! You alright?
The wings! They accumulate aether before the beast strikes!

Defeat the fiend before Otis succumbs!
Please, everyone, lend me your strength.
I have authority enough to move structures. A moment!
There... Now, please help as many as you can!
Right, let's deal with these ones first!
There are still those we can save! We keep moving!
I will make us a path. O Everkeep, hearken to me!
So many still crying out in fear and in pain... Please hold on!
Fiends too!? Damn you, Zoraal Ja!
It's up to us to stop them!
You're safe now. Be at ease.
I'm sorry for putting you through such an ordeal... It will soon be over, so please stay strong.
Deleted.
For the honor of the royal knights! Forward!
Snap out of it, Otis! Don't you recognize us!?
First formation! Show them a knight's valor!
The machines obey him!
Second formation! Seize the glory of victory!
Something about him is familiar... But...it couldn't be...
Third formation! Onward, for Alexandria!
Don't like the looks of this... Everyone, keep your guard up!
It is him─the captain of the knights!
Damn it... How do we bring him to his senses!?
If he still remembers me, then perhaps...
...protect...Her Majesty...
Apologies for the trouble I've caused.<DialoguePageSeparator>8205251</DialoguePageSeparator>So long as this body holds, I shall fight with you!
It's building up energy! Have care!
It gathers lightning to itself!
Let's split up and deal with them!
Hmph! Not holding anything back, are we?
So many... This is going to be tough.
Leave this to me!<DialoguePageSeparator>8205255</DialoguePageSeparator>Behold the bladework of a royal knight!
'Tis but a flesh wound!
Such tremendous lightning!
Not good... At this rate...
Upon mine honor, we shall weather this storm!
Now! Lay the fiend low!
Otis, you must stop! Your body can't survive this!
Nay, I cannot yield...even should it cost me my life!
Otiiis!
My queen... Are you unharmed?
Behold the bladework of a royal knight!
Greetings and good-bye.
Are you alive?
Are you happy?
Let us rise above death!
We require aether.
Do not be afraid. Death is not the end.
I will show you the worlds beyond.
Deploying drones.
Are you still alive? Activating reserve power.
Are you still alive? Disengaging safeties.
Target area delineated. Commencing erasure.
System overload. Aborting process.
Are you still alive? Recommencing erasure.
System overload. An error has occurred.
System override order confirmed.
Is this...a rift in reality? Has she lost control of the power!?
Sphene! Listen to me!
I understand, I do. And I know that you won't be swayed from your course.
But if there's truly no other way to resolve this...
Then face me! Not as a machine, but as the real you!
Lamaty'i...
Sphene!
